<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Waldsee</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Heinrich Tracht, Hans von Locheim und ihre Gesellschaft, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Fürsprache bei Johannes II. Truchseß von Waldburg wegen Herausgabe der zu Waldsee beschlagnahmten Habe und kündigt Tracht an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_240" id="119r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_240_r1l1">Der Stat cʒu Walſee </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_240_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vvir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nehſt dem Edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hanſen Truchſeſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l3">von <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> von der habe wegen / dıe hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l4">von locheim vnd <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſellſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l5">vnd cʒu euch gen walſee gefürt vnd da bekumert iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l6">die der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> von <expan>loch<ex>eim</ex></expan> von <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ſeiner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l7"><expan>geſellſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wegen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> mit <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten hie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l8">vor vns betewrt vnd behabt hat / Alſo daʒ dieſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l9">habe <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> ſey / vnd daʒ kein Auſʒman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l10">wederteil noch gemein daran niht hab / vnd <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l11"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> her <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Truchſeſʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe darauff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">no </del> den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch niht ledig gelaſſen hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l13">Als vns der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> hans von <expan>loch<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürbraht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l14">hat / 
<del rend="strikethrough">So </del> darümb auch <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Traht <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> cʒeiger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l15">dicʒ briefs der auch in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>geſellſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> iſt <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l16">kümt So <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc daʒ Jr <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l17">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gunſtige </del> gen <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hanſen <expan>Truchſ<ex>eſʒ</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l18"><expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweiſen wollet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> dıeſelb Jr habe <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ledig werde vnd vnge - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l20"><expan>hind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> volge Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_240_r1l21">Judica </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_240" id="119r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Walsee</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nehst dem edeln
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen Truchsessen
                                                von <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> von
                                                der habe wegen, die Hansen von Locheim und
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gesells<ex>chaft</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                                  <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und czu euch
                                                gen Walsee gefürt und da bekumert ist, die der
                                                  <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> von
                                                  <expan>Loch<ex>eim</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und seiner
                                                  <expan>gesellsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wegen,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, mit
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten hie vor uns
                                                betewrt und behabt hat, also daz dieselb habe
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sey und daz kein
                                                auszman weder teil noch gemein daran niht hab. Und
                                                  <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> her
                                                  <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Truchsesz
                                                  <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe darauff den
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch niht ledig
                                                gelassen hat, als uns der
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Hans von
                                                  <expan>Loch<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürbraht hat,
                                                darümb auch <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Traht
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, czeiger dicz briefs,
                                                der auch in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>gesellsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ist,
                                                  <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu euch kümt.
                                                So <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., daz ir
                                                  <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynn gen
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen
                                                  <expan>Truchs<ex>esz</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen wollet
                                                  <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> dieselb ir habe
                                                  <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ledig werde und
                                                  <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> volge. Als
                                                etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan>
                                                judica.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
